  "body": "- Inform the indications of renal biopsy and possible risk: wound bleeding (3%血尿, 1%需要輸血, 0.5%TAE, 0.01% nephrectomy & death), infection, sepsis. \n  If the patient can take the risk, we will arrange renal biopsy.    \n- Check CBC/PT/APTT, platelet function test (L72-078) before renal biopsy\n  => 開立 Echo-guided biopsy (M24-026) 併同意書, 請書記先計價且聯絡 腎臟超音波室(2437)   \n- 腎臟科fellow會開立 P71-201(SLE不用), P71-101, P71-002\n- Biopsy後, 請當科住院醫師為病人局部加壓30mins (biopsy處)"
