  "title": "Tunneled dialysis catheter/Permcath occlusion",
  "body": "-------------<< Urokinase therapy for TDC occlusion >>-------------\n- Try thrombolytic infusion treatment before HD on ---\n- Urokinse therapy is indicated but also with bleeding risks. If the patient and family can take the risks, please sign permit and arrange urokianse therapy\n  (1) Sign Urokinase thrombolytic treatment permit if no contraindication\n  (2) Check the contraindication: (a)一年內曾有顱內出血 (b)一星期內有急性出血, 如腸胃出血\n- Urokinase使用方法:\n  (1) Urokinase 240,000U in N/S 200cc, then divide in to 100cc*2 IVD in each catheter for total 1.5 hour (90 minutes) with IVAC control\n    ==> 請開立 60000U x 4pc 單位的品項泡在200cc之後.分成兩個100cc同時滴注在A端與V端\n    ==> 須使用 IVAC 控制總共滴注90分鐘後,馬上接洗腎\n    ==> 預計今晚-----洗腎,請先領藥並在下午-----開始滴, 時間請再次與洗腎室確定\n   <<<<< 請當科聯絡 HD room 何時洗腎,洗腎當天前1.5小時開始滴注Urokinase >>>>>\n  (2) 時間內未滴完的藥劑 “請勿” IV push入病人體內!!!\n  [血栓溶素(Urokinase)注射治療同意書 會在開立藥物時自己跳出來; 如果病房無法理解: 可以想像成CVC雙側接升壓劑滴注(開始不必沖管/結束接urokinase直接來洗腎室即可)\n- We will arrange hemodialysis after urokinase therapy, and then QW135 if needed in our hospital for this patient\n- Well informed the benefits and risks of hemodialysis to the family: hypotension, arrhythmia, MI, stroke, GI bleeding, ...etc\n- Please sign hemodialysis permit\n- Other choice included on new double lumen for hemodialysis. Nephrologist follow up as needed. Thanks"
